data.description: Welcome home! This charming 3 bedroom, 1 bath, two car garage home is ready for its new owners! Boasting many upgrades such as a roof that is only 1 year old, new windows, and a new hot water heater! This home is located on a great street with established homes. The kitchen offers an abundance of cabinets and a large eat in dining area. Backyard is fully fenced in for your pets! Be sure to schedule your showing on this home before its sold!
